metadata.description: The painting by Marina Deryagina, presented at the exhibition of artists in the National Museum of Art of the Republic of Mari El, became the prototype for the cover of the song "Vozvraschaisya" by the NEI artist. The official release of the track on digital platforms was in 2021. The original painting is made in oil on canvas 1100*1800mm in size and framed in a wide antique frame. When you purchase this NFT, you will receive the original track "Vozvraschaisya" in original quality and a copy of the picture in full size
